quran[63]{c,v,t}:
  76,19,Unki khidmat ke liye aisey ladke daudte phir rahey hongey jo hamesha ladke hi rahenge.Tum unhein dekho to samjho ke moti(pearls) hai jo bikhair diye gaye hain
  76,20,Wahan jidhar bhi tum nigah dalogey niyamatein hi niyamatein aur ek badi sultanat ka sar o saman tumhein nazar aayega
  76,21,"Unke upar bareek resham ke sabz libas aur atlas o deba ke kapde (rich brocade)hongey, unko chandi ke kangan pehnaye jayenge , aur unka Rubb unko nihayat pakeeza sharaab pilaeyga"
  76,22,Yeh hai tumhari jaza aur tumhari kaar-guzari qabil-e-qadr thehri hai
  76,23,"Aey Nabi, humne hi tumpar yeh Quran thoda thoda karke nazil kiya hai"
  76,24,"Lihaza tum apne Rubb ke hukum par sabr karo, aur in mein se kisi badh-amal ya munkir-e-haq ki baat na maano"
  76,25,Apne Rubb ka naam subh-o-shaam yaad karo
  76,26,"Raat ko bhi uske huzoor sajda raiz ho, Aur raat ke taveel auqat mein uski tasbeeh karte raho"
  76,27,Yeh log to jaldi hasil honay wali cheez (duniya ) se muhabbat rakhte hai aur aagey jo bhaari din aane wala hai usey nazar andaz kardetey hain
  76,28,"Humne hi inko paida kiya hai aur inke jodh bandh mazboot kiye hai, aur hum jab chahein inki shakalon ko badal kar rakh dein"
  76,29,"Yeh ek nasihat hai,ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  76,30,"Aur tumharey chahne se kuch nahin hota jab tak ke Allah na chachey, yaqeenan Allah bada Aleem-o-Haqeem hai"
  76,31,"Apni rehmat mein jisko chahta hai daakhil karta hai, Aur zalimon ke liye usne dardnaak azaab tayyar kar rakkha hai"
  77,1,Kasam hai un ( hawaon) ki jo pai dar pai bheji jati hain
  77,2,Phir toofani raftar se chalti hai
  77,3,Aur (baadalon ko) utha kar phailati hai
  77,4,Phir (unko) phaad kar juda karti hai
  77,5,Phir (dilon mei khuda ki)yaad daalti hai
  77,6,Uzar (justification) ke taur par ya daravey ke taur par
  77,7,Jis cheez ka tumse wada kiya ja raha hai woh zaroor waqey honay wali hai
  77,8,Phir jab sitarey maand (extinguish) pad jayengey
  77,9,Aur aasmaan phaad diya jayega
  77,10,Aur pahad dhunak daaley jayengey (blown away)
  77,11,Aur Rasoolon ki haziri ka waqt aa pahunchega (us roz woh cheez waqey ho jaeygi)
  77,12,Kis roz ke liye yeh kaam utha rakha gaya hai
  77,13,Faisley ke roz ke liye
  77,14,Aur tumhein kya khabar ke woh faisley ka din kya hai
  77,15,Tabahi hai us din jhutlane walon ke liye
  77,16,Kya humne aglon ko halaq nahin kiya
  77,17,Phir unhi ke pichey hum baad walon ko chalta karengey
  77,18,Mujrimo ke saath hum yahi kuch kiya karte hain
  77,19,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,20,Kya humne ek hakeer pani se tumhein paida nahin kiya
  77,21,Aur ek mukarrara muddat tak
  77,22,Usey ek mehfooz jagah thehraye rakkha
  77,23,"To dekho , hum ispar qadir thay, pas hum bahut acchi qudrat rakhne waley hain"
  77,24,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,25,Kya humne zameen ko sameth kar rakhne wali nahin banaya
  77,26,Zindon ke liye bhi aur murdon ke liye bhi
  77,27,"Aur is mein buland-o-bala pahad jamaye, Aur tumhein meetha pani pilaya"
  77,28,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,29,Chalo ab usi cheez ki taraf jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  77,30,Chalo us saaye ki taraf jo teen shaakhon(columns) wala hai
  77,31,Na thandak pahunchane wala aur na aag ki lapat se bachane wala
  77,32,woh aag mahal (castles/fortress) jaisi badi badi chingariyan phenkegi
  77,33,(Jo uchalti hui yun mehsus hongi )goya ke woh zard ount (camel) hai
  77,34,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,35,Yeh woh din hai jismein wo na kuch bolengey
  77,36,Aur na unhein mauka diya jaeyga ke koi uzr(excuse) pesh karein
  77,37,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,38,Yeh faisley ka din hai humne tumhein aur tumse pehle guzrey huey logon ko jamaa kardiya hai
  77,39,Ab agar koi chaal tum chal sakte ho to mere muqabley mein chal dekho
  77,40,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,41,Muttaqi log aaj saayon aur chashmon mein hai
  77,42,Aur jo phal woh chahein (unke liye hazir hai)
  77,43,Khao aur piyo mazey se apne un aamal ke siley mein jo tum karte rahey ho
  77,44,Hum neik logon ko aisi hi jaza detay hain
  77,45,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,46,"Kha lo aur mazey karlo thodey din, haqeeqat mein tum log mujrim ho"
  77,47,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,48,Jab inse kaha jata hai ke (Allah ke aagey) jhuko to nahin jhuktey
  77,49,Tabahi hai uss roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,50,Ab is (Quran) ke baad aur kaunsa kalaam aisa ho sakta hai jispar yeh iman layein